<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Describe an ability to provide messages array for all specified validator (without requirements to specify validator index).</p>

<p>So the code:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$validators = array(
    'month' =&gt; array(
        new Zend_Validate_Between(1, 12),
        'messages' =&gt; array(
            array(
                Zend_Validate_Between::NOT_BETWEEN =&gt;
                    'Month value %value% must be between ' .
                    '%min% and %max%',
                Zend_Validate_Between::NOT_BETWEEN_STRICT =&gt;
                    'Month value %value% must be strictly between ' .
                    '%min% and %max%'
            )
        )
    )
);
</code></pre>

<p>will be transformed to</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$validators = array(
    'month' =&gt; array(
        new Zend_Validate_Between(1, 12),
        'messages' =&gt; array(
                Zend_Validate_Between::NOT_BETWEEN =&gt;
                    'Month value %value% must be between ' .
                    '%min% and %max%',
                Zend_Validate_Between::NOT_BETWEEN_STRICT =&gt;
                    'Month value %value% must be strictly between ' .
                    '%min% and %max%'
        )
    )
);
</code></pre>

